---
/** Pricing.astro — WaaS pricing section */
---

<section class="pricing section">
  <div class="pricing__container container">
    <header class="pricing__header section-header section-header--centered">
      <h2 class="pricing__eyebrow eyebrow">WaaS — Precios</h2>
      <p class="pricing__title h2">Invierte menos, gana más con el WaaS</p>
      <p class="section-header__desc">
        No es "un sitio web barato". Es un sistema completo de adquisición de leads con soporte continuo.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="pricing__grid">
      <!-- Plan principal WaaS -->
      <article class="pricing__card pricing__card--featured card">
        <header class="pricing__card-header">
          <div class="badge">Oferta principal</div>
          <h3 class="pricing__card-eyebrow eyebrow">WaaS — Web as a Service</h3>
          <p class="pricing__card-title h3">Sistema completo de leads</p>
        </header>

        <div class="pricing__price">
          <div class="pricing__setup">
            <span class="pricing__setup-label">Setup único</span>
            <span class="pricing__setup-amount">$390</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pricing__monthly">
            <span class="pricing__amount">$270</span>
            <span class="pricing__period">/mes</span>
          </div>
          <p class="pricing__min">Contrato mínimo 6 meses</p>
        </div>

        <ul class="pricing__features" role="list">
          {[
            'Sitio web de alto rendimiento (Astro)',
            'HTML semántico + SEO técnico',
            'Core Web Vitals optimizados',
            'Diseño a medida (sin plantillas)',
            'CMS para gestión de contenidos',
            'CRM integrado para seguimiento de leads',
            'Chatbot entrenado para capturar leads 24/7',
            'Hosting y mantenimiento técnico',
            'Soporte continuo y cambios de contenido',
            'Reportes claros y entendibles',
          ].map(feature => (
            <li class="pricing__feature">
              <span class="pricing__check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
              {feature}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>

        <a class="btn btn--primary" href="/contacto">Empieza ahora</a>
        <p class="pricing__note">Si decides salir, recibes tu sitio listo en Cloudflare Pages.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- Plan high-end -->
      <article class="pricing__card card">
        <header class="pricing__card-header">
          <h3 class="pricing__card-eyebrow eyebrow">Proyecto Premium</h3>
          <p class="pricing__card-title h3">Sitio web a medida</p>
        </header>

        <div class="pricing__price">
          <div class="pricing__monthly">
            <span class="pricing__amount">$4,000</span>
            <span class="pricing__period">+</span>
          </div>
          <p class="pricing__min">Pago único · Propiedad total</p>
        </div>

        <ul class="pricing__features" role="list">
          {[
            'Sitio corporativo completo',
            'Home, nosotros, servicios, blog, contacto',
            'Arquitectura SEO y funnels',
            'Diseño 100% a medida',
            'WordPress con Etch + ACSS o Astro',
            'Integraciones a medida',
            'Propiedad total desde el día 1',
            'Entrega en 4-6 semanas',
          ].map(feature => (
            <li class="pricing__feature">
              <span class="pricing__check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
              {feature}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>

        <a class="btn btn--secondary" href="/contacto">Solicitar propuesta</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pricing__container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-space-xl);
  }

  .pricing__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: start;

    :has(> &) { container-type: inline-size; }

    @container (inline-size < 44rem) {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .pricing__card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.75rem;
    padding: 2.5rem;
  }

  .pricing__card--featured {
    border-color: rgba(56,178,240,0.4);
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(56,178,240,0.07) 0%, rgba(103,197,135,0.04) 100%);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-glow);
  }

  .pricing__card-header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .pricing__price {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    padding-block: 1.5rem;
    border-block: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .pricing__setup {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: var(--font-size-small);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .pricing__setup-label { }
  .pricing__setup-amount { font-weight: var(--font-weight-heading); color: var(--color-text); }

  .pricing__monthly {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .pricing__amount {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-heading);
    background: var(--gradient-brand);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .pricing__period {
    font-size: var(--font-size-body);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .pricing__min {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .pricing__features {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.65rem;
    list-style: none;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .pricing__feature {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.65rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    font-size: var(--font-size-small);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .pricing__check {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-block-start: 0.05em;
  }

  .pricing__note {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
</style>
